om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Hedge funds</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A few months ago, <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/36159276.193394/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb2=
1iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDItMjAvYmlsbC1hY2ttYW4tcy1zdG9ja=
3Mtd2VudC11cD9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNzIzMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0=
