-bottom: 5px;">One outcome of free markets seems to be the rise of <em>larg=
er</em> companies, and the larger and more diversified a company is, <a hre=
f=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/36159276.193394/aHR0cHM6=
