8524a319a23cB2db67f73" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targe=
t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;">the less it will be governed by price signal=
s</a>: If I mine my own ore and refine my own steel to make widgets, and th=
en use those widgets in my gizmo factory, my decisions about how many widge=
ts to make will be driven not by the price of steel or widgets, but by how =
many widgets the VP of Gizmo Factories wants and how much steel the VP of S=
teel Milling can provide.=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">In=
dex funds? When I mentioned=C2=A0<em>Red Plenty</em>, it was in the context=
 of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/36159276.19339=
